subject: Order Ratifying the Agreement between the Government of Canada and the Portuguese Republic on the Protection of Classified Information
precis: Order authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to take the actions necessary to bring into force for Canada the Agreement on the Protection of Classified Information between the Government of Canada and the Portuguese Republic, done at Lisbon on September 16, 2025.
